<p><strong>Execution environment</strong></p>
<p><strong>MuGVRE</strong> is running in a series of cloud infrastructures based at MuG partners premises (BSC, IRB Barcelona, EMBL-EBI). Physical compute clusters hosting the cloud infrastructures are physically protected and follows the security standards of hosting institutions. Direct access to the cluster are reserved to technical staff. Data transmission necessary for the internal activity of MuGVRE will use in all cases secure protocols (https, sftp). </p>
